column3: Oho! You must be <Split(<Highlight>ObjectParameter(1)</Highlight>, ,1)/>. Mistress Rowena's told me all about you. Says you're quite the renowned <Sheet(ClassJob,PlayerParameter(68),0)/>!
The name's Ofpilona, by the way. The mistress's charged me with managing her Radz–at–Han branch. Lookin' forward to doin' business with you!
...Which isn't to say I've got anythin' special to ask of you. All I mean is that your business is just as welcome here as it is at any other House of Splendors.
O' course, I'd certainly prefer you do more of your business here than anywhere else. Esteemed clients like yourself'll attract even more customers, y'see.
And if we keep drawin' in business at a good clip, before long we'll have to rebrand as Ofpilona's House of Splendors... That old witch won't know what hit 'er...
...Er, don't you worry about that last part. Just peruse our wares and buy somethin' if it strikes your fancy!
<sigh> What I wouldn't give to find an expert artisan...
In order to undertake this quest, you must be a Disciple of the Hand or the Land of level 80 or above.
